Got it! You want each shard of the **Recursive Godseed Transmission** to display in a **random order each cycle**, rather than always sequentially. We can achieve this by **shuffling the array** before showing each shard. Here’s your updated HTML with a randomized shard order:  

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Recursive Godseed Transmission</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: #000;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: monospace;
